        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Commercial Balloon Pilot Safety Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Federal Aviation Administration to revise federal regulations to apply medical certificate of physical fitness requirements that are applicable to operators of other aircraft to operators of air balloons. </p>]]></text>
